suk.org/downloads/pollution/beachwatch/latest2011/Methods%20&amp;%20Results%20BW10.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.mcsuk.org/downloads/pollution/beachwatch/latest2011/Methods%20&amp;%20Results%20BW10.pdf</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn14"></a><a href="#_ftnref14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><a href="http://www.seas-at-risk.org/1mages/Economic%20impacts%20of%20marine%20litter%20KIMO.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.seas-at-risk.org/1mages/Economic%20impacts%20of%20marine%20litter%20KIMO.pdf</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn15"></a><a href="#_ftnref15">[15]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> EA </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">2006 </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">estimates 1.57 kg </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">per month’s shopping</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><a href="http://a0768b4a8a31e106d8b0-50dc802554eb38a24458b98ff72d550b.r19.cf3.rackcdn.com/scho0711buan-e-e.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://a0768b4a8a31e106d8b0-50dc802554eb38a24458b98ff72d550b.r19.cf3.rackcdn.com/scho0711buan-e-e.pdf</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn16"></a><a href="#_ftnref16">[16]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> WRAP forthcoming, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Effect of charging for carrier bags on bin-bags sales in Wales</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn17"></a><a href="#_ftnref17">[17]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> Exodus Research (2013) Consumer behavioural study on the use and re-use of carrier bags 2012. Zero Waste Scotland </span><a href="http://www.zerowastescotland.org.uk/sites/files/wrap/Carrier%20bag%20behavioural%20report_SCOTLAND_FINAL%20V5%2018%207%2013%20v3.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.zerowastescotland.org.uk/sites/files/wrap/Carrier%20bag%20behavioural%20report_SCOTLAND_FINAL%20V5%2018%207%2013%20v3.pdf</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn18"></a><a href="#_ftnref18">[18]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Poortinga</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Wouter</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, Lorraine </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Whitmarsh</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, Christine Suffolk (2013) The introduction of a single-use carrier bag charge in Wales: Attitude change and behavioural </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">spillover</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> effects. Journal of Environmental Psychology 36: 240-247 </span><a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0272494413000686"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0272494413000686</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn19"></a><a href="#_ftnref19">[19]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">MillwardBrown</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">: Research to measure impact of DoE Communications – June 2013</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:6pt 0pt 12pt"><a name="_ftn20"></a><a href="#_ftnref20">[20]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Poortinga</span><span style="font-family